hysics\">Nobel Prize in Physics<\/a>. He is also a Russian <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Politician\" title=\"Politician\">politician<\/a> and has been a member of the Russian State Parliament, the <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Duma\" title=\"Duma\">Duma<\/a>, since 1995. Lately, he has become one of the most influential members of the <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Communist_Party_of_the_Russian_Federation\" title=\"Communist Party of the Russian Federation\">Communist Party of the Russian Federation<\/a>.<\/p>","name":"Zhores Ivanovich Alferov","place_of_birth":"Vitebsk ,  BSSR ,  Soviet Union","place_of_death":null,"text":"Zhores Ivanovich Alferov ,  born in then Soviet Union, now Belarus , Physics, 2000","year":2000.0}